Draw an angled line of a given x length.



```js
angledLineOfXLength(data: AngledLineData, sketch_group: SketchGroup, tag?: String) -> SketchGroup
```

### Examples

```js
startSketchOn('XZ')
  |> startProfileAt([0, 0], %)
  |> angledLineOfXLength({ angle: 45, length: 10 }, %, "edge1")
  |> line([10, 10], %)
  |> line([0, 10], %)
  |> close(%, "edge2")
  |> extrude(10, %)
```
